    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "14 features. 80 fixes. 20 improvements. Four Claude Code releases dropped in four days.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a39240ed4c8f65d48c383ba101a665f5921fa96c0d397a74360b28a1036fb601",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 5.6656689342403626,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Here is what actually shipped.\n\nFirst. The built in grep tool is now ripgrep.",
      "checksum": "sha256:d47a07e5a4cdd5564e9c52377a387e1decef3c23339c63ebc9f9d33b4455de80",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 5.526349206349207,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 14
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "Searching your code base just got faster, more accurate, and consistent across every operating system.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fda8234d1d1c5dc0f6261368faa27c2ea1f7dec65ebd5ec33b829ca96ca3d65a",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 5.61922902494331,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 28
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Second. The claude agents command picks up a serious flag pack.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b82fad09f98e6f866db436ae0364842b9723ce4b4f5e1fbf0ddcddaaffbe970e",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 3.7151927437641725,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 43
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "Add dir, settings, M C P config, plugin dir, and permission mode.",
      "checksum": "sha256:158a8b78a003b55ee26ca2b78863c24fffcab139bb440ef915bff5698f052328",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 4.783310657596372,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 54
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "Pin a subagent to exactly the tools and rules you want.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a0cefc44db49310d046a194d8aef66b7f1984bb5ccce9bcfa8e0f0ec055f9b2c",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 67
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "Third. The plugin marketplace finally shows per turn token cost estimates.",
      "checksum": "sha256:4c1b9daf8dc14b3295d2db80757becf8afa85d2dcf410d310c02de0803cfedc8",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 4.504671201814059,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 78
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "You see the price tag before you install.",
      "checksum": "sha256:56ac6ddc744d9a61f25a7226d3375d41e75677d466156397d67d22ad8fa45030",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 2.089795918367347,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 90
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "No more guessing what a plugin will cost you.",
      "checksum": "sha256:22c36e55418c72c357908e4aac31624c786ab0e53a157f0b0f3c85e3dba775fd",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 2.2755555555555556,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 98
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Fourth. The rewind menu adds Summarize up to here.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b5ff8e8654eca1fb09ea59c2eea0aa16aaf1a44bb9338ad160fedbc6cba22e03",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 3.297233560090703,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 108
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "Compress the old turns, keep the recent ones.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fd9a642d3638c9c991b9b74eb5b2bf0bdf570788877a6a0507ae42aa9da2b477",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 2.5541950113378684,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 117
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "Long sessions stop bleeding tokens. Fifth.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1295c1e959a531958448abd91d45b265f4fb51c2e3ce7b4ea4a9356669c7f318",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 125
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "Hooks now emit terminal sequences directly from JSON output.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9dd3b726ffe24fafb4d307bf6d5d77001b6bb715409583af78d14ab2bbd0f9c7",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 3.5294331065759637,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 131
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "Notifications, window titles, even bells.",
      "checksum": "sha256:19517d9cbca246862798d7b8efa34da4ae5dbb20ec1d4536dadc88e125ad9ab8",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 2.414875283446712,
      "word_count": 5,
      "words_offset": 140
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "No T T Y required. Sixth. Background sessions finally survive a Mac going to sleep.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a95f5c4e741edc1e08b1fade57e083cc52dad37fcaaeee792d21f106d34a2660",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 5.061950113378685,
      "word_count": 15,
      "words_offset": 145
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "The daemon catches clock jumps on wake, and your model and effort level persist across the resume.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1ede7c7badb39f4b20c2c4ac63a4eaf363b59f6b0b6541990b3d0743be32c458",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 6.03718820861678,
      "word_count": 17,
      "words_offset": 160
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Ripgrep, claude agents flags, or plugin price tags.",
      "checksum": "sha256:efc8d5671955d50ff84e3234c5d196c5e31e9087c553ac30ccc4ea79e412b735",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
